{"tid":1196874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盧偉聰：示威者破壞香港良好理性示威傳統　強調會追究","createTime":"2019-06-10T00:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T00:33:53.000Z","uid":32577,"like":2,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1efc9b042d1fd9ace76f57b211d46f59c1f88d82","tid":1196874,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:19:42.000Z","msg":"警務處處長盧偉聰表示，示威者衝擊立法會的行動並無意思，亦感到非常遺憾，他說有3名警員受傷，警方並非磨心。<br />\n<br />\n他嚴厲譴責有關暴力行為，昨晚有戴上口罩的暴力示威者，在沒有理由下，衝擊立法會，形容有關行為亦非為表達意見，破壞香港良好理性的示威傳統，強調會追究，警方會逐步清場。<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461789-20190610.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461789-20190610.htm&d=OwzbFhxxS8LWxL2ugy7iTDDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=7d22464e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461789-20190610.htm&h=9e606f30\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461789-20190610.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f3350efd03d60c97824ce44cfa96f8556afe9498","tid":1196874,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:20:33.000Z","msg":"話會翻睇所有傳媒既片，串到"},{"pid":"f09dc09efe06b378064f3eeb2c446f08e342cfad","tid":1196874,"uid":79302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:20:46.000Z","msg":"屌你咩 理性示威而家有撚用呀"},{"pid":"559fc082fd4bfb203c66c1e3c8c853dc0fae0c09","tid":1196874,"uid":79302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:21:18.000Z","msg":"你啲警犬拉入出去又點計呀"},{"pid":"dd36675835b6b295940a93a71a3d4d19449cbf3a","tid":1196874,"uid":7323,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:21:38.000Z","msg":"他說有3名警員受傷，警方並非磨心。<br />\n<br />\n黑警就係維穩既工具"},{"pid":"08df2c070148d5c8b186b3bb922d4a706047056f","tid":1196874,"uid":206533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:23:39.000Z","msg":"叫黑警唔係無理由。<br />\n黑心，黑人憎。"},{"pid":"65497c58a751a6a4277a643c6415845a5bd8a5